ect page: Wales and Western Cultural Fusion (sharepoint.com). For all other support please contact your HR Business Partner.\",\"aboutTheRole\":{\"essential\":[\"Work Plan production and resource optimization skills\",\"Scheduling profile in work planning/scheduling system\",\"Core Planning Skills Level 2\",\"Knowledge of access and possession processes and systems\",\"Safe System of Work Planning Process and System\",\"Good interpersonal, communication  and organizational skills\"],\"desirable\":[\"Knowledge of maintenance delivery processes and techniques\"],\"keyAccountabilities\":[\"Plan and optimize all agreed work activities for the section.\",\"Accurately update systems, databases and records as required.\",\"Produce Safe System of Work plans.\",\"Submit green zone access and isolation requests.\",\"Produce draft quarterly plans.\",\"Manage weekly Plan-Do-Review meetings.\",\"Represent Section Managers at planning meetings.\",\"Collate and maintain infrastructure maintenance records.\"]}}"